skins.shipDescription: New Orleans-class heavy cruiser ¨C Quincy, hull number CA-39.
skins.selfIntroduction: I am Quincy, the New Orleans-class heavy cruiser. I'm not fond of fighting... It'd be better if everyone could help each other out...
skins.acquisition: C-Commander... Pleased to meet you... I'm the New Orleans-class heavy cruiser, Quincy. Um, since we're going to be living together from now on, is there anything I can help you with?
skins.login: Commander, is there something I can help with...?
skins.details: Being stared at like this... is really embarrassing...
skins.secretaryIdle2: Um, sorry... I'm not really sure how to turn people down... Besides, isn't it good to make others happy...?
skins.secretaryIdle3: I'll have you know that I've turned down plenty of requests before! For example... uhh... umm, I can't think of any right now...
skins.secretaryTouch: I'm not used to this whole "physical contact" thing, but if it's a request from the Commander, then...
skins.secretarySpecialTouch: C-commander... e-even I can get mad!

skins.shipDescription: Everyone's so cheerful and energetic... Commander, um, if you're tired, want to rest here with me?
skins.acquisition: Everyone's so cheerful and energetic... Commander, um, if you're tired, want to rest here with me?
skins.details: I'll just stay here and help watch everyone's belongings. Uh... I'm really not very good with exercise...
skins.secretaryIdle1: It feels like... everyone is staring at me when I wear a swimsuit... It's so embarrassing...
skins.secretaryIdle2: Beverages? Don't worry, I came prepared.
skins.secretaryIdle3: Listening to the sounds of the sea really puts me at ease...
skins.secretarySpecialTouch: *Whimper*... Could you please not do stuff like this in front of everyone...?
